#         (newer dashboards call this the "secret" key — click "Reveal" to
#          see it. Long token starting with eyJ...)
#
# ⚠ The service_role / secret key bypasses ALL security rules. SERVER ONLY.
#   Never paste it into the mobile app or any browser code, and don't share
